I don't see many Viktor's around so i don't have a very accurate profile. But from my experience Viktor's usually make small retorts after killing someone like 'why try?' and 'tough luck bud' but apart from that wont say vey much, however if you try to take a jab at them they always have a short truthful comeback that completely shuts down the person insulting them.
Viktors are cocky, not mean cocky but the cocky of: 'you've got a handgun, but I've got a 44. magnum.'

hope that helps :p {{champion:112}}

